title: Avengers: Earth's Mightiest Heroes Magazine (2011) #1
description: Captain America, Iron Man, Thor, Giant-Man, Wasp, Black Panther, Hawkeye and the Incredible Hulk. They are the Avengers: Earth's Mightiest Heroes! Join them in this giant-sized comic based on the hit animated series on Disney XD as they battle some of the world's deadliest villains: the Super Adaptoid, the Crimson Dynamo, the Winter Guard, the Mad Thinker and Ultimo — as well as Baron Zemo, the Enchantress and the rest of the Masters of Evil! Collecting AVENGERS: EARTH'S MIGHTIEST HEROES #1-4.
